Aquarius is a mineral sports drink manufactured by The Coca-Cola Company .
It was first introduced in 1983 in Japan as a sports drink .
It was introduced to Spain and Portugal in 1991 , and it became the official drink of the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona .
Aquarius is available in Argentina , Belgium , Brazil , Iceland , Indonesia , Ireland , Italy , Japan , Luxembourg , Morocco , and Portugal .
Flavors include carrot orange , citrus , honey lemon , lemon , orange , watermelon , and Coca-cola .
This drink is known to be created for sports people after doing exercise , but also it is great for any other kind of people , as it 's refreshing .
